ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35132030a766ce4991b28dacb878116a696ce746","tid":1294984,"uid":113458,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aaf4e3790f9d34a69791943ae7fd33f5c43ea3c0","tid":1294984,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"依家正常的人都用Flutter寫手機apps<br />\n但我仲用React Native,算唔算廢人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"Why ? Facebook , Microsoft 都用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"之前Airbnb 做咩棄坑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"佢個篇文章列左好多原因。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為最大的factor係人的因素（devs 唔鐘意 JavaScript)<br />\n<br />\n之後當Airbnb 出左篇文後，Facebook 已經好積極咁fix。<br />\nPerformance 果d亦都係可以解決的問題（佢地會refactor 個bridge）<br />\nJavaScript果邊，亦都可以用TypeScript 去 mitigate <br />\n<br />\n係Microsoft，有好多rating 唔錯的apps 都係用RN 重寫某部分可以shared ge code <br />\n<br />\n坦白講，用咩野technology 係好depends on usecase。<br />\n如果你想web同mobile share 同個codebase，react native 係一個好好的選擇 (eg: UberEat)<br />\n<a href=\"https://eng.uber.com/ubereats-react-native/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feng.uber.com%2Fubereats-react-native%2F&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=7ec9aa8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eng.uber.com/ubereats-react-native/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係好討厭JavaScript，Xamarin ，Flutter 都係唔錯的cross platform choice"},{"pid":"db9d07a79b207fb6fe3d9bdbc3766131bb25a67c","tid":1294984,"uid":113458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaf4e3790f9d34a69791943ae7fd33f5c43ea3c0","tid":1294984,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"依家正常的人都用Flutter寫手機apps<br />\n但我仲用React Native,算唔算廢人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"無話廢唔廢，只要果個technology 能夠幫你用最少的resource 去寫到隻好app就得"},{"pid":"1fc28125f388409aa0ae27075fd82a2d85747354","tid":1294984,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:3